        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 3 at 2:03PM CDT by NWS Norman OK</headline>
        <description>At 203 PM CDT, Doppler radar indicated a strong thunderstorm near
Kremlin, moving northeast at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations in or near the path include...
Kremlin...                        Pond Creek...
Lamont...
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
